//How to create Landing Page?
Step-1
----------
-	In HV Link DashBoard, click on “Add New” button
-	You will see a form
-	Fill up form (Name, Description, Slug) below way 
a.	Upload (500x500) image
b.	Name: Get FREE Netflix Gift Card
c.	Description: write a description on it
d.	Slug: write KeyWord

-	Click on “Get Started” button to save

Step-2
----------
-	When you click on “Get Started” button, You will see below Offer link page
-	Click on “+ Add Link” , you will see a form
 
Title: GET THIS OFFER
URL: copy offer link from CPA and paste here
Highlight this link	(Enable it)

Click on “Save” button to save

-	Design:  click on “Design” button to choose template design
 
a.	Select a design
b.	Show Quick Bio Credit (Disable it)
c.	Display Share Button (Disable it)
Click on “Save” button to save

-	Setting: click on “Setting” button to add Cover picture
 
a.	Profile, click on “Edit” icon
 
Select a cover picture (820x360px)
b.	Click on “Save” button to save

You will see a proper Landing Page. If you need, change desigh template and see output
 






